regen.absent_element: Export functionality for SQL query results
regen.new_specification: The system shall provide the capability to export the results of SQL queries to a CSV file for external use.

regen.absent_element: Constraints or conditions for map selection and list generation
regen.new_specification: The system shall clearly define and implement constraints and conditions under which projects are selected based on the map and project list is generated, ensuring functionality stability and reliability.
The system shall provide visual feedback on the map when a project is selected, indicating the selection to the user.

label: SQL errors will be reported to the user for correction.
